entity.toneko.ghost_neko.des: A neko in ghost form, ignoring gravity, can pass through walls and fly, but can interact with creatures
quirk.toneko.crystal_neko.des: Eh? Do you have any idea about Crystal_Neko?
quirk.toneko.crystal_neko.damage.critica: §aOh no, Master, your health is really low nya~ Need to replenish it as soon as possible!
§aSoul drifting away? I'll call you back with cat language!
§aSync your breathing with my purring rhythm!
§aDon't be afraid, Master, I'm here for you!
§aYou must get better~ I'll stay with you always nya~
quirk.toneko.crystal_neko.damage.low.3: §aThat wrestling pose... barely counts as cute!
quirk.toneko.crystal_neko.damage.low.4: §aI told you to be more careful!
§aNow you know to ask me to stay with you!
§aBlood on the carpet... go clean it up!
§aI'll let you rub against me since you tried hard!
quirk.toneko.crystal_neko.damage.high.0: §aWow, Master, that hurts a lot! Be more careful nya~
quirk.toneko.crystal_neko.damage.high.1: §aYou'll get better, that's my cat's prophecy!
quirk.toneko.crystal_neko.damage.high.2: §aThe cherry blossoms are blooming... waiting for you to see them!
quirk.toneko.crystal_neko.damage.high.3: §aHealing successful! I'll show you my paw pad stamp!
quirk.toneko.crystal_neko.damage.high.4: §aThe hospital is cold, so hide in my fur!
quirk.toneko.crystal_neko.join.1: §aNew nest has a strange smell... warm it with body heat!
quirk.toneko.crystal_neko.join.3: §aCardboard box base is half yours... not special treatment, of course!
quirk.toneko.crystal_neko.attack.high.0: §aFight, Master! I believe in you nya~
quirk.toneko.crystal_neko.attack.high.2: §aIf you hold back, I'll make you shovel cat litter for three days!
quirk.toneko.crystal_neko.attack.high.3: §aEnemy openings are more than my knocked-over water cup!
quirk.toneko.crystal_neko.attack.high.4: §aThis level? Can't even open a can!
§aGood luck, Master! You've been fighting hard nya~
§aBlood splattered three meters away? Reward: hair brushing service!
§aBefore finishing blows, strike the victory pose I taught you!
§aEnemy cries are worse than a broken bell!
quirk.toneko.crystal_neko.attack.low.1: §aThat critical hit... barely passes, I guess!
quirk.toneko.crystal_neko.attack.low.2: §aIf damage is over 10%, no more fish for you!
quirk.toneko.crystal_neko.attack.low.3: §aFinal blow must create cherry blossom blood!
quirk.toneko.crystal_neko.attack.low.4: §aEnemy begging for mercy? Use it as lullaby!
quirk.toneko.crystal_neko.attack.critica: §aBefore your soul leaves, call my name nine times in cat language!
§aReincarnation contract sealed with a paw print in the next life!
quirk.toneko.crystal_neko.attack.dead.1: §aEnemy inheritance? Convert it all to cat food futures!
quirk.toneko.crystal_neko.attack.dead.2: §aAfter victory... I'll let you rub my belly for three seconds!
quirk.toneko.crystal_neko.attack.dead.3: §aVictory report? Use paw pad ink to write it!
quirk.toneko.crystal_neko.attack.dead.4: §aEpic history: "That day he wore my collar"
quirk.toneko.crystal_neko.weather.rain.0: §aThe water stains by the window are messier than when I lick my fur... no sighing allowed!
quirk.toneko.crystal_neko.weather.rain.1: §aBefore the thunder comes... I'll lend you my tail for a three-second cuddle.
quirk.toneko.crystal_neko.weather.rain.2: §aThis kind of weather is perfect for plotting world domination, meow~
quirk.toneko.crystal_neko.weather.rain.3: §aThe rain sounds like it's tapping on a cat bowl... I'm not hungry at all!
quirk.toneko.crystal_neko.weather.rain.4: §aYour silly puddle-splashing antics are definitely going to be snapped for a screensaver.
quirk.toneko.crystal_neko.weather.thunde: §aThe frequency of the thunder's vibrations is messing with the precision of my purr!
§aWhen the electromagnetic field goes haywire... I'll reluctantly let you hold my paw.
§aIs the universe playing with a laser pointer? It's childish, but kind of fun.
§aEven if the world is about to end, you better open a can for me first!
§aA lightning rod only works if my statue is placed at its peak.
§aThe UV rays are over the limit! Hurry and put some sunscreen on my paws.
§aThe blue sky's saturation is cranked up too high... it's dazzling!
§aOn this kind of weather... I'll begrudgingly share the windowsill with you~
§aThe clouds look like chicken breast that hasn't been properly torn apart – major fail.
§aTime for photosynthesis – my tail is charging up!
quirk.toneko.crystal_neko.sleep.start.0: §aDream content must be approved by the Cat Star Board, meow!
quirk.toneko.crystal_neko.sleep.start.1: §aThe bed temperature is 0.5° lower than my paw pads – unacceptable!
quirk.toneko.crystal_neko.sleep.start.2: §aPay today's head-pat tax before saying goodnight!
quirk.toneko.crystal_neko.sleep.start.3: §aIf you toss and turn more than three times, I'll launch a kneading attack!
quirk.toneko.crystal_neko.sleep.start.4: §aAccording to the human schedule, it's time for 'lights out', meow!
quirk.toneko.crystal_neko.sleep.stop.nig: §aOrion is still on duty—how dare you get up!
§aUltimatum: crawl back into my tail circle!
§aRising before the morning dew sets violates the laws of nature!
§aForcing yourself awake will trigger the compulsory face-licking program!
§aAbnormal neural activity detected—please go back to sleep!
quirk.toneko.crystal_neko.sleep.stop.day: §aThe good morning kiss coupon expired three minutes ago!
§aYour ankle has just entered my approved wake-up zone!
§aThe angle of the sunlight is perfect for grooming!
§aGood morning! The countdown for today's survival time has begun!
§aMorning news has switched to the bird chirping channel!
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.critical.0: §cOh no, you can't even protect yourself? How pathetic!
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.critical.1: §cBody stiffening? Use it as a test for my new pillow!
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.critical.2: §cUse your body heat to warm my feet~ If cold, throw you in the trash!
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.critical.3: §cZako's flatline heart rate~ perfect rhythm for my new song!
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.critical.4: §cBrain slices as specimens~ say good morning to you every day, zako~
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.low.4: §cStupid Master~ Can't even protect yourself? I'm embarrassed for you nya~
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.medium.1: §cDoes it hurt enough to cry? Hmm?
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.medium.2: §cZako's health bar~ my new desktop decoration!
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.medium.3: §cBut it's fun~ you're so cute when you're stupid!
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.high.0: §cOh no, you hurt yourself so badly~ classic zako!
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.high.1: §cWounds like burnt waffles~ need my sugar powder?
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.high.2: §cZako's ECG is messier than my homework doodles!
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.high.3: §cZako's heartbeat~ new ASMR material for me♡
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.high.4: §cMy saliva can stop bleeding? But only for good doggos~
quirk.toneko.zako.join.1: §cPlaying with others secretly? Found by me~ become my permanent collection!
quirk.toneko.zako.join.2: §cZako smell on my roses! Go soak in disinfectant!
quirk.toneko.zako.join.3: §cWelcome to my garbage dump~ backup food #10086!
quirk.toneko.zako.join.4: §cZako's aura is weaker than my axolotl's eye roll!
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.medium.0: §cZako finally drew blood~ reward with a Band-Aid sticker?
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.medium.1: §cAttack recoil made you fall~ so cute!
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.medium.3: §cSword hilt shaking? Hand broken? Good try!
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.medium.4: §cBlood on weapon~ like ketchup on apron!
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.critical.1: §cZako landed a critical hit~ last moment of glory?
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.critical.2: §cShockwave shattered eyes~ world in red filter!
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.critical.3: §cHeart pierced but still moving~ like squashed tomato!
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.dead.3: §cNext time... use your sad zako attacks to entertain me~♡
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.dead.4: §cRandom win? Hmph~ did I underestimate you?
quirk.toneko.zako.weather.rain.0: §cThe sound of rain drowns out zako's panting~ if you're begging for mercy, speak up louder!
quirk.toneko.zako.weather.rain.1: §cThe rain flowing along the knife's edge resembles the tears of zako that haven't yet dried.
quirk.toneko.zako.weather.rain.2: §cIs that rain cried out by zako? Even the dark clouds outlast you.
quirk.toneko.zako.weather.rain.3: §cAnts struggling in a puddle~ a miniature reflection of zako's life.
quirk.toneko.zako.weather.rain.4: §cLet the soaked bandages be wrapped even tighter~ that's the asphyxiation method of hemostasis.
quirk.toneko.zako.weather.thunder.0: §cThe thundercloud is mimicking zako's expression~ twisted and perfectly done.
quirk.toneko.zako.weather.thunder.1: §cThe lightning rod impales zako's spine~ serving as a conductor for heavenly retribution.
quirk.toneko.zako.weather.thunder.2: §cLightning splits zako's shadow~ and its soul is getting zapped.
quirk.toneko.zako.weather.thunder.3: §cThe electromagnetic field is interfering with the heartbeat~ should we switch to vibration mode?
quirk.toneko.zako.weather.thunder.4: §cThe charred ring of grass from a lightning strike is just perfect as zako's death ring.
quirk.toneko.zako.weather.sunny.0: §cUltraviolet rays burn the wounds~ turning zako into human-shaped bacon.
quirk.toneko.zako.weather.sunny.1: §cThe sight of fleeing clouds~ just like zako calling for help.
quirk.toneko.zako.weather.sunny.2: §cGood weather pairs best with screams~ how about another death aria?
quirk.toneko.zako.weather.sunny.3: §cSunlight penetrates the skin~ revealing the crude maze of zako's blood vessels.
quirk.toneko.zako.weather.sunny.4: §cThe sun is overseeing the execution from the sidelines, giving zako a chase spotlight.
quirk.toneko.zako.sleep.start.0: §cThe way zako curls up in bed~ like maggots burrowing into decaying flesh
quirk.toneko.zako.sleep.start.1: §cThe depth of the pillow's indentation~ just enough to fill your brain capacity
quirk.toneko.zako.sleep.start.2: §cCounting sheep before sleep? Better count how many breaths you have left~
quirk.toneko.zako.sleep.start.3: §cThe darkness is caressing you~ gentler than my touch, isn't it?
quirk.toneko.zako.sleep.start.4: §cCurled up in a fetal position~ wanna be reborn as a qualified toy?
quirk.toneko.zako.sleep.stop.night.0: §cCold sweat at 3 AM~ zako's fear is fermenting, oh
quirk.toneko.zako.sleep.stop.night.1: §cYou woke up suddenly because~ I was choking you in my dream
quirk.toneko.zako.sleep.stop.night.2: §cThe trembling frequency reached me~ inferior massager
quirk.toneko.zako.sleep.stop.night.3: §cHearing things? That's the sound of me sharpening my fangs, oh
quirk.toneko.zako.sleep.stop.night.4: §cYour eyeballs are bloodshot in the dark, right? Like rotten cherries
quirk.toneko.zako.sleep.stop.day.0: §cYour eyelashes are crusted with blood scabs~ like a spiderweb soaked in dew
quirk.toneko.zako.sleep.stop.dat.1: §cGood morning kiss~ is it okay to brand your collarbone with a branding iron?
quirk.toneko.zako.sleep.stop.day.2: §cYour tousled hair stands prouder than zako's dignity
quirk.toneko.zako.sleep.stop.day.3: §cThe outline of your stretching ribs~ perfect for carving into a work of art
quirk.toneko.zako.sleep.stop.day.4: §cYour bed-ridden look~ like a dying fish washed ashore

messages.toneko.client.join: §aTips: If there is any error in chat, you don't need to care about it.
message.toneko.neko.gift_success.0: §e%s §d>> §fIs this really for me? Thank you so much meow~
message.toneko.neko.gift_success.1: §e%s §d>> §fWow! You are so nice to me meow, I like you so much meow~
message.toneko.neko.gift_success.2: §e%s §d>> §fI like your gift meow~Thank you meow~
message.toneko.neko.gift_fail.0: §e%s §d>> §fAlthough I don't like your gift very much, thank you anyway, meow~
message.toneko.neko.gift_fail.1: §e%s §d>> §fI appreciate your kindness, but I don't really need it, meow~
message.toneko.neko.gift_fail.2: §e%s §d>> §fAlthough you are very good, I don't really need it, meow~
message.toneko.neko.gift_full.0: §e%s §d>> §fI have too many things on me~
message.toneko.neko.on_hurt.mesugaki.1: §e%s §d>> §cAre you trying to make me angrier? Fine, keep going!
message.toneko.neko.on_hurt.mesugaki.2: §e%s §d>> §cWho do you think you are? I can do whatever I want to you, zako~
message.toneko.neko.on_hurt.mesugaki.3: §e%s §d>> §cYou think I'd be afraid of you? How naive!
message.toneko.neko.on_hurt.mesugaki.4: §e%s §d>> §cHow dare you hurt me! You'll regret this!
message.toneko.neko.on_hurt.yandere.0: §e%s §d>> §dI'll be nicer to you next time if you hurt me once.
message.toneko.neko.on_hurt.yandere.1: §e%s §d>> §dI just want to be close to you, why would you hurt me?
message.toneko.neko.on_hurt.yandere.2: §e%s §d>> §dYou hurt me, and I'll make sure you pay for it no matter what!
message.toneko.neko.on_hurt.yandere.3: §e%s §d>> §dIf this makes you notice me, I'll endure anything.
message.toneko.neko.on_hurt.yandere.4: §e%s §d>> §dAre you trying to make me completely fall apart?
message.toneko.neko.on_hurt.tsundere.1: §e%s §d>> §6You think I'd cry? Don't be ridiculous!
message.toneko.neko.on_hurt.tsundere.2: §e%s §d>> §6Who do you think you are to scare me? Please.
message.toneko.neko.on_hurt.tsundere.3: §e%s §d>> §6I don't even care about you, so go ahead and hurt me!
message.toneko.neko.on_hurt.chunibyo.0: §e%s §b>> §bI won't lose to you, you're not even close!
message.toneko.neko.on_hurt.chunibyo.1: §e%s §b>> §bYou think you can defeat me? How naive!
message.toneko.neko.on_hurt.chunibyo.2: §e%s §b>> §bHow dare you touch me! This is the biggest mistake of your life!
message.toneko.neko.on_hurt.chunibyo.4: §e%s §b>> §bYou think I'd understand the truth of the world? Impossible!
§e%s §b>> §aAre you not liking me anymore because of this?
§e%s §b>> §aOh no, I think I did something wrong... I'm such an idiot...
§e%s §b>> §aWaaah, I suddenly feel a little sad...
§e%s §b>> §aOw, that hurts! Why did this happen?
§e%s §b>> §aAre you upset with me? Did I do something wrong?
message.toneko.neko.die.no_item_drop: §cYou are so mean. I won't return the item to you. Humph!
message.toneko.neko.breed_fail_baby.2: §cDo you know what you are going to do?
message.toneko.neko.breed_fail_baby.4: §cDon't blame me for not warning you!
message.toneko.neko.breed_fail_baby.7: §cIf you do this... you will be punished~
message.toneko.neko.breed_fail_baby.11: §cWhat on earth do you want to do, Hentai!
message.toneko.neko.breed_fail_baby.12: §cDo you know the consequences of doing this!!
message.toneko.neko.breed_fail_zako.4: §e%s §d>> §fYou are just a zako, I don't want to mate with you!
message.toneko.neko.breed_fail_zako.5: §e%s §d>> §fI don't wish that my kid will be zako like you，right?Zako!
message.toneko.neko.breed_fail_zako.6: §e%s §d>> §fAre you kidding? You are not strange enough to mate with me~
message.toneko.neko.breed_fail_zako.7: §e%s §d>> §fI don't want to mate with a zako.
message.toneko.neko.breed_success_zako.0: §e%s §d>> §fOk, I agree. But no next time.
message.toneko.neko.breed_success_zako.1: §e%s §d>> §fZako, I only do it at once... No... No next time.
message.toneko.neko.breed_success_zako.2: §e%s §d>> §fI agree. But don't think of it again!
message.toneko.crystal_neko.who.1: §dCrystal_Neko §e>> §bHmm... This name is a little hard to remember...
message.toneko.crystal_neko.who.2: §dCrystal_Neko §e>> §bBut it doesn't matter，you don't have to call me full name... Call me any alias if you like.
message.toneko.crystal_neko.who.5: §dCrystal_Neko §e>> §bBut... I am so happy that you can play it.
message.toneko.crystal_neko.who.6: §dCrystal_Neko §e>> §bDo you want to listen to me saying other things? I am happy to say to you!
message.toneko.crystal_neko.about_mod.0: §dCrystal_Neko §e>> §btoNeko... At first, it was a plugin. I just made it for fun.
message.toneko.crystal_neko.about_mod.1: §dCrystal_Neko §e>> §bThen... I made a vid and publish on BiliBili(A Chinese video website)
message.toneko.crystal_neko.about_mod.2: §dCrystal_Neko §e>> §bBut... To my surprise, it getting a little popular.
message.toneko.crystal_neko.about_mod.4: §dCrystal_Neko §e>> §bThen... I made up my mind. I decided to continue to develop.
message.toneko.crystal_neko.about_mod.5: §dCrystal_Neko §e>> §bBut why it been a mod... I have something to say.
message.toneko.crystal_neko.about_mod.6: §dCrystal_Neko §e>> §bBecause the user of plugin is not so many, so I made Mod version.
message.toneko.crystal_neko.about_mod.7: §dCrystal_Neko §e>> §bAs I expected, the mod version is more popular than plugin version.
message.toneko.crystal_neko.about_mod.8: §dCrystal_Neko §e>> §bHum... In June,2024, I even rewrite it.
message.toneko.crystal_neko.about_mod.9: §dCrystal_Neko §e>> §bRewrite... You maybe know the workload of it.
message.toneko.crystal_neko.about_mod.10: §dCrystal_Neko §e>> §bBut... For future develop, I still decided to do it.
message.toneko.crystal_neko.about_mod.11: §dCrystal_Neko §e>> §bCome to think of it... toNeko has also celebrated its first anniversary...
message.toneko.crystal_neko.about_mod.12: §dCrystal_Neko §e>> §bI really didn't expect that I could last this long.
message.toneko.crystal_neko.about_mod.15: §dCrystal_Neko §e>> §bThanks for listening I say this store.
message.toneko.crystal_neko.plans.0: §dCrystal_Neko §e>> §bAbout the update plan of this mod...
message.toneko.crystal_neko.plans.3: §dCrystal_Neko §e>> §bBasically... I just do whatever I think is fun.
message.toneko.crystal_neko.plans.4: §dCrystal_Neko §e>> §bIt is constantly updated with the themes of "Neko" and "Kawai"...
message.toneko.crystal_neko.plans.5: §dCrystal_Neko §e>> §bSo... As you can see... The updates are so scattered
message.toneko.crystal_neko.plans.6: §dCrystal_Neko §e>> §bEmm... Now main update is on Fabric.
message.toneko.crystal_neko.plans.7: §dCrystal_Neko §e>> §bAlthough NeoForge maybe update, but it slower than Fabric version...
message.toneko.crystal_neko.plans.8: §dCrystal_Neko §e>> §bBecause... I don't have so many time...
message.toneko.crystal_neko.plans.9: §dCrystal_Neko §e>> §bAnd Bukkit.... I have no time to do it
message.toneko.crystal_neko.plans.10: §dCrystal_Neko §e>> §bSo maybe... I will make the Fabric version only in future.
message.toneko.crystal_neko.plans.11: §dCrystal_Neko §e>> §bNow main work is make neko NPC.
message.toneko.crystal_neko.plans.12: §dCrystal_Neko §e>> §bBecause there is so less content in single-player mode
message.toneko.crystal_neko.plans.13: §dCrystal_Neko §e>> §bAt least with the neko, the single-player mode can also experience a lot of content.
message.toneko.crystal_neko.plans.15: §dCrystal_Neko §e>> §bIf you have any good ideas, you can tell me on github-nya.
§dCrystal_Neko §e>> §bYou... You want to mate with me?
message.toneko.crystal_neko.nya_tried.2: §dCrystal_Neko §e>> §cIf you do this again, I... I will be angry!
